00:54:01.520 --> 00:54:04.630
Somebody did debug this for me, though.
He pointed out, you could go into the wine

00:54:04.630 --> 00:54:06.859
cellar and drink the wine and leave the bottle.
[ Laughter. ]

00:54:06.859 --> 00:54:12.900
